Package: mlcvi
Type: Package
Title: Machine Learning-Based Cultural Values Inventory (ML-CVI)
Version: 0.3.1
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Gary", "Leng",
      email = "gary-h.leng@polyu.edu.hk",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Implements the machine learning-based cultural values inventory
    (ML-CVI) for cross-cultural research. Provides tools for computing cultural
    distance between countries via the Kogut-Singh, Shulgin, and ML-CVI methods,
    screening cultural value mediators using Sobel tests, and imputing
    missing country-level indicators via Ridge regression weighted by
    ML-CVI feature importances.
